{"tid":623831,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"覺唔覺華語電影主題曲屌打香港電影嗰啲","createTime":"2018-04-10T10:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T17:06:48.000Z","uid":6842,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7d24ee7a897539b53bdd984c8d5672a7690dbb","tid":623831,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"事源呢排聽緊hebe首愛了很久的朋友，發覺香港電影好少出啲好歌<br />\n<br />\n嗱台灣愛情片嘅歌大部分都勁紅 呢幾年有那些年、等一個人、小幸運、聽見下雨的聲音、星空、不能說的秘密 到最近嘅 幾分之幾、愛了很久的朋友同 我們<br />\n<br />\n大陸拍嘅電影都有什麼歌、讓我留在你身邊呢啲(利申唔熟 應該仲有啲都係好hit嘅歌）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話香港噏得出嘅有幾多首吖？ 許志安首remember me係cover嘅，謝安琪首歌聲如初係幫印度電影宣傳 真係香港本土電影音樂我淨係數得出上年supper首沙燕之歌 俾盡你 加埋首公廁mk情歌長相廝守 <br />\n我想講嘅係 覺唔覺香港電影音樂好撚可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfdbe8ae6942c7845e68408473b0be8d55d91c5","tid":623831,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"光年之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f023c8a383ca52bf8a2a457d916dea3b859a715","tid":623831,"uid":181294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6be7381aea23cf17df28c5cede88117e9d34df74","tid":623831,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"滄海一聲笑"},{"pid":"f6f10b2e4890113a428095b77847ce7501c09734","tid":623831,"uid":6842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f023c8a383ca52bf8a2a457d916dea3b859a715","tid":623831,"uid":181294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱聽咗次，係ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f99e68a184aa78d5e12c4724ff9b317458966f","tid":623831,"uid":181294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪